data.name: label7.Text
data.value: As for calorie burning during yoga, it varies based on factors like style, intensity, and individual attributes. On average, a one-hour session can burn about 150-300 calories for someone weighing around 150 pounds, with higher rates possible in more intense or extended sessions.

data.name: lblWalkingDescription.Text
data.value: Yoga is a mind-body practice that combines physical postures, breathing exercises, and meditation or relaxation techniques. It originated in ancient India and has since become popular worldwide for its numerous health benefits.
